script.name: !ship.cmd.trade.dist.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$PAGE.ID = 6020
gosub sub.GetVars $homebase = $a.obj -> get homebase
if $a.state == [MEvent.Start] $table.data = table alloc $array = array alloc: size=0 $table.data['run'] = $array if $homebase -> exists $array = array alloc: size=0 $table.data[$homebase] = $array $array = $table.data['run'] $cmd.table = table alloc $new.array = create new array, arguments=$homebase, $cmd.table, null, null, null append $new.array to array $array end set global variable: name='trade.dist.data' value=$table.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] if $menu.id == 'menu' if $selection == 'clear.all' $array = array alloc: size=0 $table.data['run'] = $array gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'load.previous' $previous.run = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='egosoft.tdist.last' $data = clone array: $previous.run $table.data['run'] = $data gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'save.run' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2130 $input = create input: id='save.run.name', user input=Var/String, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input else if $selection == 'load.run' gosub sub.BuildProfileMenu return $input else if $selection == 'delete.run' gosub sub.BuildProfileMenu return $input end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' if $selection == 'add' if $value != $a.obj AND $value $array = $table.data['run'] $cmd.table = table alloc $new.array = create new array, arguments=$value, $cmd.table, null, null, null append $new.array to array $array gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $selection == 'docked.ship.menu' if $value -> exists $array = $table.data['run'] $cmd.table = table alloc $new.array = create new array, arguments=$value, $cmd.table, null, null, null append $new.array to array $array gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $selection == 'add.docked.carrier' if $value -> exists $carrier = $value gosub sub.BuildDockedMenu return $input end
else if $selection == 'add.ship' if $value != $a.obj AND $value if not $a.obj -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay if not $value -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $speak = get text id: ware=Transporter Device $speak.arr = create new array, arguments=[Page.ObjDesc], $speak, [Page.MiscVoice], 24, null START speak array: $speak.arr prio=10 gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end $array = $table.data['run'] $cmd.table = table alloc $new.array = create new array, arguments=$value, $cmd.table, null, null, null append $new.array to array $array gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $selection == 'load.run' if $value $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' if $saved.runs $array = $saved.runs[$value] $data = clone array: $array $table.data['run'] = $data end end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $selection == 'delete.run' if $value $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' if $saved.runs remove key $value from table $saved.runs end end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $selection == 'replace' $i = $table.data['replace'] $data = $table.data['run'][$i] $data[0] = $value gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $selection == 'save.run.name' if $value $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' if not $saved.runs $saved.runs = table alloc set global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' value=$saved.runs end $array = $table.data['run'] $data = clone array: $array $saved.runs[$value] = $data START speak text: page=13 id=1382 priority=10 gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $selection == 'commands' gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $menu.id == 'commands' if $selection == 'new.cmd.ware' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $ware = $value[0] $amt = $value[1] $cmd = $table.data['new.cmd'] $array = array alloc: size=4 $array[0] = $cmd $array[1] = $amt $array[2] = [FALSE] $price = get average price of ware $ware $array[3] = $price $cmd.table[$ware] = $array $input = create menu return to previous menu: value='update' return $input end else if $selection == 'change.amt' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $ware = $value[0] $amt = $value[1] $cmd.table[$ware][1] = $amt gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu return $menu end else if $selection == 'change.price' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $ware = $value[0] $amt = $value[1] $tmp = $cmd.table[$ware][3] $amt = $tmp + $amt $cmd.table[$ware][3] = $amt gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu return $menu end else if $selection == 'commands' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $value[0] if $value == 'update' gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu return $menu end else if $value == 'cmd.dump' $array = array alloc: size=4 $array[0] = $value $array[1] = 0 $array[2] = [FALSE] $array[3] = 0 $cmd.table[-1] = $array gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu return $menu end end else if $menu.id == 'delete.run' if $selection == ' ' else $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' if $saved.runs AND $value == [Button.Yes] if $saved.runs[$selection] remove key $selection from table $saved.runs gosub sub.BuildProfileMenu return $menu end end end end
else if $a.state == 'selection' $menu.id = $a.value[0] $value = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' $dest = convert serialised string to object: string=$value if $dest -> exists $table.data['selected'] = $dest else $table.data['selected'] = null end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Hotkey] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' if $selection == 'dest.info' $dest = convert serialised string to object: string=$value $input = create input: id='objinfo' object info page, object=$dest return $input end else if $menu.id == 'load.run' OR $menu.id == 'delete.run' if $selection == 'profile.delete' $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$PAGE.ID textid=2134, $value, null, null, null, null $title = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2135 $input = create input: id=$value, message box=$read.text, title=$title, buttons=[Buttons.YesNo], icon=60, default button=[Button.Yes] return $input end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Context] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $menu.id == 'menu' $dest = $value[1] $i = $value[2] $value = $value[0] if $value == 'info' $input = create input: id='objinfo' object info page, object=$dest return $input else if $value == 'remove' $array = $table.data['run'] remove element from array $array at index $i gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'replace' $array = $table.data['run'] $table.data['replace'] = $i if $a.obj -> get amount of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='replace', user input=Var/Ship/Station owned by Player, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=Player, flags=[Find.NoSound], default=null else $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='replace', user input=Var/Station/Carrier to dock at, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=Player, flags=[Find.NoSound], default=null end return $input else if $value == 'move.up' $array = $table.data['run'] $run.data = $array[$i] remove element from array $array at index $i dec $i = insert $run.data into array $array at index $i gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'move.down' $array = $table.data['run'] $run.data = $array[$i] remove element from array $array at index $i inc $i = insert $run.data into array $array at index $i gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'cmds' $table.data['dest'] = $i gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu return $input end else if $menu.id == 'commands' $ware = $value[1] $selection = $value[0] if $selection == 'remove' remove key $ware from table $cmd.table else if $selection == 'wait.yes' $cmd.table[$ware][2] = [TRUE] else if $selection == 'wait.no' $cmd.table[$ware][2] = [FALSE] else if $selection == 'change.cmd' $value = $value[2] $cmd.table[$ware][0] = $value else if $selection == 'amount' gosub sub.ChangeAmount return $input else if $selection == 'price' gosub sub.ChangePrice return $input end gosub sub.BuildCommandMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end
else if $a.state == 'new.cmd' $table.data['new.cmd'] = $a.value $sub.Val = $a.value gosub sub.GetAvailableWares gosub sub.GetWare return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.cmd' gosub sub.GetCommand return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.docked' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='add.docked.carrier', user input=Var/Station/Carrier to dock at, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=[Find.NoSound], default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.ship' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='add.ship', user input=Var/Ship owned by Player, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=Player, flags=[Find.NoSound], default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='add', user input=Var/Station/Carrier to dock at, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=[Find.NoSound], default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'menu' if $a.value == 'startcmd' return [TRUE] end else if $a.state == [MEvent.Arguments] $array = $table.data['run'] $a.obj ->set local variable: name='egosoft.tdist.last' value=$array $ret = create new array, arguments=$array, null, null, null, null return $ret
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Finished] gosub sub.ClearVars end
return null
sub.BuildDockedMenu: $menu = create custom menu array $docked.ships = $carrier ->get ship table from sector/ship/station $sorted.array = null if $docked.ships $table = table alloc $key = get next key: table=$docked.ships key=null while $key $ship.owner = $key -> get true owner do if $ship.owner == Player $table[$key] = $key $key = get next key: table=$docked.ships key=$key end do if size of table $table $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$table end if $sorted.array $i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.array while $i < $size $key = $sorted.array[$i] $text = $key -> get name add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$key inc $i = end else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text end
set menu option: $menu, icon=56
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2059 $input = create input: id='docked.ship.menu' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$carrier callback=null endsub
sub.GetAvailableWares: if $sub.Val == 'cmd.load' OR $sub.Val == 'cmd.fill' if $dest -> is of class Ship $ware.table = $dest ->get wares table: include equipped=[FALSE] else $ware.table = $dest ->get products table: include equipment=[FALSE] if $dest -> is of class Complex Hub $inter.wares = $dest ->get complex intermediate wares if $inter.wares $ware.itr = size of array $inter.wares while $ware.itr dec $ware.itr = $ware = $inter.wares[$ware.itr] if $dest ->can sell intermediate ware: ware=$ware $ware.amt = $dest -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.table[$ware] = $ware.amt end end end end end else if $sub.Val == 'cmd.unload' OR $sub.Val == 'cmd.stock' $array = $table.data['run'] $table = $table.data['commands'] @ $ware.table = $a.obj -> call script !lib.distribute.getwares : Run Array=$array Destination ID=$dest.id if $dest -> is of class Factory $table = $dest ->get primary resources table $table2 = $dest ->get secondary resources table $table = merge tables, $table, $table2, null, null, null $ware = get next key: table=$ware.table key=null while $ware $next = get next key: table=$ware.table key=$ware skip if $table[$ware] remove key $ware from table $ware.table $ware = $next end end end endsub
sub.BuildProfileMenu: $menu = create custom menu array $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' if $saved.runs $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$saved.runs $i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.array while $i < $size $name = $sorted.array[$i] add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$name returnvalue=$name inc $i = end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=60 set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.ScriptDelete], id='profile.delete' set menu option: $menu, input context=[Context.ScriptSelect]
$text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2129 $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2131 $input = create input: id=$selection menu=$menu title=$text description=$read.text callback=null endsub
sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array $menu.selected = $table.data['selected'] if $menu.selected -> exists
end
$read.text = get command info: command=COMMAND_TRADE_DISTRIBUTE add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2052 $text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=20301 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $read.text, $text, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='add' value=null $text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=50301 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $read.text, $text, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='add.ship' value=null $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102551 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $read.text, $text, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text nextinput='add.docked' value=null
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2053 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=-50 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns = create new array, arguments=$text, null, null, null, null $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2054 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text append $text to array $text.columns add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.columns
$array = $table.data['run'] if size of array $array $size = size of array $array $i = 0 while $i < $size $dest.id = $i $dest = $array[$i][0] $cmd.table = $array[$i][1] $context = create context menu $ret = create new array, arguments='info', $dest, $i, null, null $read.text = read text: page=35 id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=29, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] gosub sub.AddContextInfo add context menu separator: menu=$context
$ret = create new array, arguments='replace', $dest, $i, null, null $read.text = read text: page=35 id=1109 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=113, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] gosub sub.AddContextInfo
$disabled = [FALSE] *do if $homebase AND $i == 0 *$disabled = [TRUE] $ret = create new array, arguments='remove', $dest, $i, null, null $read.text = read text: page=35 id=1107 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=66, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=null, disabled=$disabled gosub sub.AddContextInfo $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2055 add context sub menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=37, disabled=[FALSE] gosub sub.AddContextInfo $ret = create new array, arguments='move.up', $dest, $i, null, null $disabled = [FALSE] do if $i == 0 $disabled = [TRUE] $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2056 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=37, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=null, disabled=$disabled $ret = create new array, arguments='move.down', $dest, $i, null, null $disabled = [FALSE] do if $i == ( $size - 1 ) $disabled = [TRUE] $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2057 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=37, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=null, disabled=$disabled add context end sub menu entry: menu=$context add context menu separator: menu=$context $ret = create new array, arguments='cmds', $dest, $i, null, null $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2058 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=40, returnvalue=$ret, hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] gosub sub.AddContextInfo $text = $dest -> serialise object $ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$text, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE] inc $i = $text = sprintf: fmt='%s.', $i, null, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=30 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns = create new array, arguments=$text, null, null, null, null $text = $dest ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=30 length=12 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text append $text to array $text.columns $text = create custom menu column string, position=42 length=-50 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$dest append $text to array $text.columns $value = size of table $cmd.table $value = convert number $value to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$value append $text to array $text.columns
add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.columns returnvalue=$ret end else $read.text = read text: page=35 id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text end
$read.text = read text: page=1904 id=1015 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text
$array = $table.data['run'] $size = size of array $array
$previous.run = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='egosoft.tdist.last' if $previous.run if size of array $previous.run $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2127 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='load.previous' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret end end
if $size > 0 $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2109 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='clear.all' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret end
add section to custom menu: $menu
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2128 if $size > 1 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='save.run' else set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id='save.run' end add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2129 $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1100006 $saved.runs = get global variable: name='egosoft.tdist.saved' $saved.runs.count = 0 if $saved.runs $saved.runs.count = size of table $saved.runs end $text = sprintf: fmt='[%s: %s]', $text, $saved.runs.count, null, null, null $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text if $saved.runs.count > 0 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='load.run' else set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id='load.run' end add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$ret if $saved.runs.count > 0 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='delete.run' $text = read text: page=[Page.Input] id=14 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$ret end add section to custom menu: $menu
if $size > 1 $ret = 'startcmd' else set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id='startcmd' end $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=250 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret
* add info at bottom $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2132 $text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2063 $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text if $size < 1 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $run.i = 1 $i = 0 while $i < $size $dest = $array[$i][0] $cmd.table = $array[$i][1] inc $i = $read.text = get command name: command=COMMAND_DOCKAT $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $read.text, $dest, null, null, null $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = $dest ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[1] = $text set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Normal] add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text.columns inc $run.i =
if $cmd.table[-1] if $cmd.table[-1][2] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 end $text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2133 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text.columns[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[1] = $text set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Grey] add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text.columns inc $run.i = end
$sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$cmd.table $ware.i = 0 $ware.size = size of array $sorted.array while $ware.i < $ware.size $ware = $sorted.array[$ware.i] inc $ware.i = $cmd = $cmd.table[$ware][0] $amt = $cmd.table[$ware][1] $wait = $cmd.table[$ware][2] $read.text = null if $cmd == 'cmd.unload' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2067 else if $cmd == 'cmd.stock' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2071 end
if $read.text $text = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s %s', $read.text, $amt, $ware, null, null if $wait $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 end $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[1] = $text set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Grey] add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text.columns end end
$ware.i = 0 while $ware.i < $ware.size $ware = $sorted.array[$ware.i] inc $ware.i = $cmd = $cmd.table[$ware][0] $amt = $cmd.table[$ware][1] $wait = $cmd.table[$ware][2] $read.text = null if $cmd == 'cmd.fill' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2069 else if $cmd == 'cmd.load' $read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2065 end
if $read.text $text = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s %s', $read.text, $amt, $ware, null, null if $wait $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 end $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[1] = $text set menu line option: $menu, text colour=[MenuColour.Grey] add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$text.columns end end end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=60 set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.Identity], id='dest.info'
$read.text = read text: page=$PAGE.ID id=2050 $text = read text: page=2010 id=100030 $input = create input: id='menu' menu=$menu title=$text description=$read.text callback=[Callback.Selection] endsub
sub.AddContextInfo: if $dest -> is of class Ship $read.text = read text: page=35 id=721 add context menu info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$dest else if $dest -> is of class Station $read.text = read text: page=1904 id=20301 $text = $dest -> get name add context menu info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$text end $read.text = read text: page=35 id=1104012 $sector = $dest -> get sector add context menu info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$sector $value = $table.data['run'][$dest.id] $value = $value[1] $value = size of table $value $value = convert number $value to string $read.text = read text: page=1904 id=1015 add context menu info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$value endsub
